verbose_text: Downregulation of transcription factor PROX1 in esophageal squamous cell carcinoma (ESCC) inhibits cellular proliferation and migration; high expression of PROX1 in ESCC could be used as an indicator of poor prognosis [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: transcription factor PROX1 in esophageal squamous cell carcinoma (ESCC) inhibits cellular proliferation
